<tr>
  <td class="innerpadding">
    <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
      <tr>
        <td class="bodycopy h3">
          <%= @user.first_name %>,
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="bodycopy">
          Only 1.5 weeks to go to complete ‘<%= link_to @experiment.name, experiment_url(id: @experiment.slug, category: @experiment.category, utm_source: "experiment_midway", utm_medium: "email"), class: "inline-link" %>’!<br><br>
          This is a perfect moment to reflect on the impact this experiment has had on your life so far.<br><br>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="bodycopy">
          <strong>Have you noticed any of these benefits?</strong><br>
          <ul>
            <% @experiment.benefits.each do |benefit| %>
            <li><%= benefit.name %></li>
            <% end %>
          </ul>

          And have there perhaps been other changes you’ve noticed in the past 1.5 weeks? <br><br>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td class="bodycopy">
          Take a bit of time to think about this, so that you’re better able to decide whether this experiment
          is moving you into the right direction.<br><br>

          Keep up the good work, changing habits is not easy!<br>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
      <tr>
        <td class="bodycopy" style="padding: 20px 0 10px 0;">
          <em>P.S. If you’ve decided not to continue this experiment right now, make sure to <%= link_to 'cancel it', dashboard_experiments_url(utm_source: "experiment_midway", utm_medium: "email"), class: "inline-link" %> so that you can retry it later.</em><br><br>

          Love,<br>
          Marlies
        </td>
      </tr>

    </table>
  </td>
</tr>
